4-3:3.1 Binary occurrence, constant containment and disjointness of documents We show in this section, that the frequency based noise probability n(t) N in the idf definition can be explained as a total probability with binary term occurrence, constant document containment and disjointness of document containments .
4-4:We refer to a probability function as binary if for all events the probability is either 1.0 or 0.0 .
