7-1:INFORMATIVE We showed in the previous sections that the disjointness assumption leads to frequency based probabilities and that the independence assumption leads to Poisson probabilities .
7-2:In this section, we formulate a frequency based definition and a Poisson based definition of the probability of being informative and then we compare the two definitions .
